docs {
  # Mint Fungible Token
  
  Mints additional supply to an existing fungible token.
  
  ## Request Body
  - `tokenId` (string, required): The ID of the fungible token to mint (e.g., "0.0.123456")
  - `amount` (number, required): The amount of tokens to mint (must be at least 1)
  
  ## Response
  - `success` (boolean): Whether the operation was successful
  - `data` (object):
    - `newTotalSupply` (string): The new total supply after minting
    - `transactionId` (string): The Hedera transaction ID
    - `receipt` (object): The transaction receipt from Hedera
  
  ## Notes
  - The token must have been created with `TokenSupplyType.Infinite` (or a higher max supply than current)
  - The account performing the mint must have the supply key
  - The amount is added to the current supply
  - The database is automatically updated with the new total supply
}
